quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  108,1,"Verily, We have granted you (O Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم) Al-Kauthar (a river in Paradise).",footnotes:337678:1
  108,2,"Therefore turn in prayer to your Lord and sacrifice (to Him only)."
  108,3,"For he who hates you (O Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم), he will be cut off (from posterity and every good thing in this world and in the Hereafter).",footnotes:337681:1
